Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
Its a good thing.  I wouldnt have met some of my closest friends if i hadnt been forced to share a bathroom with them.  I think freshman halls are an experience that all students should have.  you get to meet a ton of people you wouldnt normally meet.